data.description: This fantastic, nearly new, condominium in a desirable water front neighborhood is close to Brunswick airport, shopping and golf.  This move-in ready end unit features stainless steel appliances, granite countertops, plenty of storage and covered parking for two cars. Fabulous community pool overlooking Troupe Creek. Magnificent views of the marsh and coastal waterway from the deck and bedroom.
